  "3320840": {
    "name": "Odile: Black Duckling Tale",
    "steam_appid": 3320840,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Merhen Fantasy Action Adventure 'Odile: Black Duckling Tale' is a game that becomes a little duck and grows up by taking away human power and collects multi-endings. Its main features include pretty dot graphics, fairytale-like stories, and interaction with NPCs with fun movements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple controls using only the keyboard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Movement:</strong> Arrow keys (Up, Down, Left, Right) / + Shift (Run)<br><strong>Action:</strong> Z (Jump), X (Dodge), C (Attack), V (Transform)<br><strong>Fast Forward:</strong> Tab<br><strong>Skip:</strong> Esc</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320840/extras/f25e5d509f6c4eb2297571a6bf2d84dd.avif?t=1764695011\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320840/extras_big/f25e5d509f6c4eb2297571a6bf2d84dd.avif?t=1764695011 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The full-fledged game begins when a black duck being bullied in the woods follows one of a princess, a shaman, or a hunter into town. Who would you join?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320840/extras/302739fe4683eaf1fbf32bfa340aceb4.avif?t=1764695011\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320840/extras_big/302739fe4683eaf1fbf32bfa340aceb4.avif?t=1764695011 width=800 height=292 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320840/extras/176f1b13cee876967d68ed5eb24f1a6f.avif?t=1764695011\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320840/extras_big/176f1b13cee876967d68ed5eb24f1a6f.avif?t=1764695011 width=800 height=292 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320840/extras/e611d2f34eb11090f349c51b134a12b5.avif?t=1764695011\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320840/extras_big/e611d2f34eb11090f349c51b134a12b5.avif?t=1764695011 width=800 height=333 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320840/extras/5c61c85ab57048824b6b67c99d298dec.avif?t=1764695011\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320840/extras_big/5c61c85ab57048824b6b67c99d298dec.avif?t=1764695011 width=800 height=343 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manipulate the black duck to take human energy. Taking up a lot of energy can kill humans, and sometimes witnesses. If you let them run scared, the black duck could be in danger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320840/extras/b6feddf883375434e08d939724d7c7c4.avif?t=1764695011\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320840/extras_big/b6feddf883375434e08d939724d7c7c4.avif?t=1764695011 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Normally no one notices the little duck's covert behavior, but sometimes there are attack NPCs that see through the duck's black magic, resulting in a battle. Run up, down, jump, and roll to avoid the attack.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320840/extras/40a38e5ed07192c8f573869e2262765c.avif?t=1764695011\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320840/extras_big/40a38e5ed07192c8f573869e2262765c.avif?t=1764695011 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While 'Odile' is a story-heavy game, most of the text is delivered through the NPC's speech bubble without stopping gameplay. SCG dialogue events only come at a level where the story does not interfere with gameplay and helps you immerse yourself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perform belt-scrolling action on three stages: the palace, the temple, and the tavern.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And experience 28 multi-endings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can now play through the <i>Palace Route</i>, <i>Temple Route</i>, and Pub<i> Route</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect all <strong>28 different endings</strong> that await you depending on your choices!</p>",
